subject: Soccer
World Cup (Soccer)
lead_paragraph: Inter Milan and Barcelona have agreed to swap strikers Zlatan Ibrahimovic and Samuel Eto’o, but Ibrahimovic is continuing to play for Inter while the players negotiate new contracts.
